metadata.name: Level.0 STAR CUB NFT #1
metadata.description: Level.0 STAR CUB NFT is a collection including 9999 Octopuses created by GameBoy, a gamefi aggregator platform. Octopus owners will get a discount on any game NFT asset on the GameBoy platform. And by participating in the game (upcoming soon) through level.0 octopus as pass, you can fight with other octopuses to unlock more surprises.Join us: Official website Get your octopus and unlock the mysteries of the deep sea!
